description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '10-Day Standing Cardio Workout Challenge' from the channel Roberta's Gym.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Today's workout is quite challenging and would need you to perform these exercises all while standing up. These cardio exercises will help you burn fat in 10 days all while doing this for 15 minutes everyday!

Routines such as the Forward Jump, Spilt Jumps, and the Jumping Jacks will surely make you catch your breath but they're very helpful in burning body fat and strengthening your muscles. Routines like the Arm Circles help balance things out. Make sure you utilize the rest times, they're helpful in making this weight loss process work!
